replies.text:
Hi, the error is because React ^18.1.0 breaks the dnd. To fix this you need to downgrade React to ^17.0.2.

1) Delete node_modules

2) Edit package.json dependencies with the following versions:
"react": "^17.0.2"
"react-dom": "^17.0.2"
"@testing-library/react": "^12.1.1",
"@testing-library/user-event": "^12.5.0"

3) Edit index.tsx

import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import './index.css';
import App from './App';

ReactDOM.render(
	<React.StrictMode>
		<App />
	</React.StrictMode>,
	document.getElementById('root')
);

4) npm i

That worked for me, I hope this helps.

